            h1#books-title.books__title Books
            .books__description
               p Welcome to Bookify, where captivating reads await. Explore bestselling thrillers, heartwarming romances, and more across diverse genres.
               p Discover new favorites and timeless classics. Start your literary journey today.
         section#about.about(aria-labelledby='about-title')
            h1#about-title About
            p At Bookify, we're passionate about connecting readers with captivating stories and enriching content. 
            p With a commitment to curating diverse genres and highlighting both established authors and emerging voices, we strive to create an immersive reading experience for book lovers worldwide. 
            p Our mission is simple: to inspire, entertain, and ignite imaginations through the power of literature. 
            p Join us on our journey as we celebrate the magic of storytelling and the joy of discovery. Welcome to Bookify.
         section#contact.contact(aria-labelledby='contact-title')
            h1#contact-title Contact us
            form.form(action="/" method="post")  
               input.form__input.form__input--email(type="email" name="email" placeholder="example@gmail.com" maxlength="255" required)
               input.form__input.form__input--tel(type="tel" name="telephone" placeholder="9286211252" maxlength="10" pattern="[0-9]{3}[0-9]{3}[0-9]{4}" required)
               textarea.form__textarea(name="message" maxlength="255" placeholder="Message here..." required) 
               button.form__button Send

